{"tid":368212,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台南定花蓮","createTime":"2017-08-21T11:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T10:45:51.000Z","uid":54834,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b83a227f380ba2b8eeebea7b529d484c81d2e0","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"諗咗好耐 仲未有決定<br />\n臨開學想嚟次獨遊<br />\n因為生活上有啲野好煩所以想一個人hea下散下心 仲有睇下景<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問咁多位去台南定花蓮好？<br />\n兩個都未去過<br />\n之前只係去過台北 台中同高雄<br />\n預去四日到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262dc5422e76f32fbbb8e255d99d38993e84f277","tid":368212,"uid":26223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:44:03.000Z","msg":"散心去花蓮，舒服，又靚"},{"pid":"03dcb3a1cad1f4ac4a4b17dda08d1edfc677c53f","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散心去花蓮，舒服，又靚</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打先<br />\n但一個人去又無車牌會唔會好麻煩<br />\n包車又好貴 同其他人夾車坐又好似限死咗自己啲時間<br />\n同埋上網睇過花蓮啲景點好似好散咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c433d6c6fb651edc1021c1b5f46b6c6e86c2e76","tid":368212,"uid":130907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得台南好悶好熱，咩文青之地、慢生活呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 網上吹大左。安平區都係一般，個樹屋幾無聊下，可以玩下街邊的攤位打發時間。觀汐平台唔錯，幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外物價平，食物唔錯，不過預好多排隊店。飲碗牛肉湯、買條蛋糕都要等半個鐘以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無咩做可以等下。"},{"pid":"21906e34efcf284fae4423ba058b9cba5d50f84f","tid":368212,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:50:04.000Z","msg":"花蓮冇得輸<br />\n上次一個參加左當地一日團，好多後生女女參加都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4f8e2f6c3974aadd1e1e8005bcfb9dcf689e51","tid":368212,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"台南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhea吓行吓古蹟，行到攰就坐低食吓嘢，間間都好食咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完又可以踩吓單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6caa0727d69645d3841600f5adf2d22ec569dbd2","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得台南好悶好熱，咩文青之地、慢生活呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 網上吹大左。安平區都係一般，個樹屋幾無聊下，可以玩下街邊的攤位打發時間。觀汐平台唔錯，幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外物價平，食物唔錯，不過預好多排隊店。飲碗牛肉湯、買條蛋糕都要等半個鐘以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無咩做可以等下。</blockquote><br />\n唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台南都好似預睇古蹟多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想係市內踩單車周圍行下唔知可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7cead0a851d1dbf739f3f2ef8b97b88d251f47","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>花蓮冇得輸<br />\n上次一個參加左當地一日團，好多後生女女參加都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日團我都諗過<br />\n不過我唔想啲時間限死唒(對唔住我有啲麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n因為我好中意自己一個對住個海放空發下夢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc20ea6390d095eba282a698ea4067410b2ba56","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhea吓行吓古蹟，行到攰就坐低食吓嘢，間間都好食咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完又可以踩吓單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問單車可唔可以去到市內七八成景點<br />\n同埋會唔會好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c77313878b0fb9cfcd31e78845b2f1c7600b86e","tid":368212,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>花蓮冇得輸<br />\n上次一個參加左當地一日團，好多後生女女參加都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日團我都諗過<br />\n不過我唔想啲時間限死唒(對唔住我有啲麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n因為我好中意自己一個對住個海放空發下夢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟團主要係帶你去太魯閣<br />\n你住花蓮行5 ～10分鐘 就係太平洋 好方便<br />\n正到嘔"},{"pid":"6f16c791eefd5b0e7ae2dbd7ffb13481c62c25ec","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>花蓮冇得輸<br />\n上次一個參加左當地一日團，好多後生女女參加都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日團我都諗過<br />\n不過我唔想啲時間限死唒(對唔住我有啲麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n因為我好中意自己一個對住個海放空發下夢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟團主要係帶你去太魯閣<br />\n你住花蓮行5 ～10分鐘 就係太平洋 好方便<br />\n正到嘔</blockquote><br />\n都係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果單車遊o唔ok㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7300bc4e765e52252f8d0d4dbc70e60134e52ca1","tid":368212,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim