faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d444a069458330788e7573dc4f94d3bee028415","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:39:05.000Z","msg":"題外話<br />\n八個月內去3次台灣好似好密(怕比屋企人屌)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家會唔會覺得好密<br />\n上兩次就係去唒台北中高雄<br />\n如果獨遊仲有咩好提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c52affad9884377894c638ddf3b237725b86f1","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>凈係去過花蓮.....冇車確係唔太方便<br />\n推介住Airbnb.....可以免費借單車.....又平又好住屋主又好人</blockquote><br />\n巴打上次踩單車？</blockquote><br />\n係花蓮市內先踩咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n花蓮留左兩日咋.....都係坐觀光巴士.....等車等到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都想知下個邊既道路環境</blockquote><br />\n都係踩馬路架.....自己小心囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望無事"},{"pid":"7945b9d7f361a63a9cf08c8aff65f3c48f5c1dc4","tid":368212,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"見有人講信用咭（定係宜家要改叫卡？）<br />\n<br />\n轆咭有些商號張簽賬單上會問你轆咩貨幣，<br />\n通常係台幣加另一種，例如港幣/美元咁。<br />\n<br />\n其實係間舖既結算銀行offer俾你既rate。<br />\n如果你係台灣，記得揀用台幣。<br />\n<br />\n外幣rate通常西到冇人有。<br />\n<br />\n其他國家我唔太清楚<br />\n台灣post就淨係講台灣轆咭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位繼續返原本話題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85415bdea0a52185084c9217b1aeb62120d35b8f","tid":368212,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201