:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:24:14.000Z","msg":"花蓮無得輸，怕交通麻煩可以比多個選擇你<br />\n台東其實都ok 巴士個個景點都經 同埋都密<br />\n<br />\n花蓮七星潭、清水斷崖、太魯閣<br />\n夜晚係七星潭就咁望天聽住啲海浪聲已經好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7735cc60e8f9a0cd7e39f38ed80e222ab4e505d8","tid":368212,"uid":104081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:32:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5fb3153da9219f698c46aa7f4f03a2a1bcca090","tid":368212,"uid":115081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人在花蓮第六日。<br />\n我會揀花蓮，東華大學去七星潭洗鬼半個鐘，我係火車站出發七星潭電動車15m搞掂。我有間民宿都ok。家的感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家花蓮天氣如何 聽日飛 好驚打風上唔到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6869ca061f8d340741e25c1f91d844d4027f2520","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T02:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見有人講信用咭（定係宜家要改叫卡？）<br />\n<br />\n轆咭有些商號張簽賬單上會問你轆咩貨幣，<br />\n通常係台幣加另一種，例如港幣/美元咁。<br />\n<br />\n其實係間舖既結算銀行offer俾你既rate。<br />\n如果你係台灣，記得揀用台幣。<br />\n<br />\n外幣rate通常西到冇人有。<br />\n<br />\n其他國家我唔太清楚<br />\n台灣post就淨係講台灣轆咭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位繼續返原本話題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該絲打提供資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732134bb5dcc267b1d0ee755d2153ad563b58f49","tid":368212,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我八月頭去完，用佢obike 個app申請account, 再俾USD49 訂金(有學生證就USD19)就可以用佢架單車<br />\n個人覺得幾方便<br />\n到時唔用可以申請refund</blockquote><br />\n係咪用信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\